body: Hello there @nemothekid, the issue there is that your sLabel field is an unexported value, making it SLabel instead of sLabel, makes in unmarshal-able. Please see https://play.golang.org/p/pmsIs2GW0O, The Unmarshal docs talk about it that Unmarshal will only set exported fields. Also we use the issue tracker for tracking bugs, you can post questions on the mailing list https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/golang-nuts.
